otland in 1296. The Treaty of Edinburgh was signed in 1328 which declared peace between the two kingdoms and brought the war to an end.","jurisdictionLevel":0},{"id":1705193,"age":42,"year":"1337","toYear":"1453","julianDay":2209390,"title":"The Hundred Years' War","description":"The Hundred Years' War between France and England was largely due to the question of legitimate succession to the French crown.","jurisdictionLevel":0}],"lifeSummary":"Agnes was born about 1295, in England. She had at least 1 son with Walter Risby. She died after 1371, in her hometown."},"et":{"about 1295–after 1371":"umbes 1295–pärast 1371","1285–1371":"1285–1371","–1361":"–1361","1317–Male":"1317–Surnud","1295–1371":"1295–1371","1285":"1285","1295":"1295","1361":"1361","1371":"1371","1337":"1337","1315":"1315","by 1371":"1371","1453":"1453","after 1371":"pärast 1371","about 1295":"umbes 1295","about 1361":"umbes 1361","1317":"1317","1328":"1328","Risby, Suffolk, England":"Risby, Suffolk, England","England":"England","Mildenhall, Suffolk, England":"Mildenhall, Suffolk, England"},"fi":{"about 1295–after 1371":"noin 1295–1371 jälkeen","1285–1371":"1285–1371","–1361":"–1361","1317–Male":"1317–Kuollut","1295–1371":"1295–1371","1285":"1285","1295":"1295","1361":"1361","1371":"1371","1337":"1337","1315":"1315","by 1371":"1371","1453":"1453","after 1371":"1371 jälkeen","about 1295":"noin 1295","about 1361":"noin 1361","1317":"1317","1328":"1328","Risby, Suffolk, England":"Risby, Suffolk, England","England":"England","Mildenhall, Suffolk, England":"Mildenhall, Suffolk, England"},"fr":{"about 1295–after 1371":"environ 1295–après 1371","1285–1371":"1285–1371","–1361":"–1361","1317–Male":"1317–Décédé","1295–1371":"1295–1371","1285":"1285","1295":"1295","1361":"1361","1371":"1371","1337":"1337","1315":"1315","by 1371":"1371","1453":"1453","after 1371":"après 1371","about 1295":"environ 1295","about 1361":"environ 1361","1317":"1317","1328":"1328","Risby, Suffolk, England":"Risby, Suffolk, Angleterre",